Before:

```bash
vendor\bin\php-cs-fixer fix src/file.php
## no config file used, damn it!
```

```bash
vendor\bin\php php-cs-fixer fix src/file.php --config=.php_cs.dist
Loaded config from ".php_cs.dist" ## cool!
```

After:
```bash
vendor\bin\php php-cs-fixer fix src/file.php
Loaded config from ".php_cs.dist" ## cool!
```
